---
import SectionPageLayout from "../layouts/SectionPageLayout.astro";
---

<SectionPageLayout
  title="Sakai Plus | Sakai LMS"
  description="Add Sakai to your enterprise LMS with Sakai Plus and extend teaching with open learning tools."
  kicker="Sakai Plus"
  heading="Plug Into The Future Of Learning"
>
  <article class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-[var(--sakai-paper)] p-6">
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">
      Sakai has always been great for learning. With Sakai Plus, institutions can add Sakai capabilities to an existing enterprise LMS.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">
      Using LTI Advantage, Sakai Plus accepts enrollment data from enterprise LMS platforms and synchronizes grades seamlessly.
      This gives innovative instructors richer learning content and authentic assessment options without a full platform replacement.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">
      Sakai is seeking institutions to become beta testers and help shape Sakai Plus to meet higher-education teaching needs.
    </p>
  </article>

  <section class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <a href="https://www.sakailms.org#dataItem-kjepe8tj" class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="sans text-xl font-black uppercase text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">Talk with the Sakai team about Sakai Plus and beta participation.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.sakailms.org/try-sakai-lms-free" class="hard-border block-shadow-soft bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="sans text-xl font-black uppercase text-[var(--sakai-ink)]">Try Sakai</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--sakai-ink-soft)]">Explore Sakai directly while evaluating Sakai Plus options.</p>
    </a>
  </section>
</SectionPageLayout>
